comment: Johnson (LAC) sets the screen on Rubio (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Prince (MIN) sets the screen on Johnson (LAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LATR and LHH show that Johnson (LAC) makes contact with Wiggins' (MIN) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) makes incidental contact with Jordan (LAC) that does not affect his ability to defend.
Towns (MIN) and Jordan (LAC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Paul (LAC) and Prince (MIN) make incidental contact with one another while jumping for the rebound.
Johnson (LAC) commits a take foul on Rubio (MIN).
Jordan (LAC) makes incidental contact with Rubio (MIN) as he comes to set the screen.
L-SLA shows that Paul (LAC) places two hands on Rubio (MIN) and affects his RSBQ prior to the foul call on Redick (LAC).
Redick (LAC) makes contact with Rubio's (MIN) arm and body that causes him to fall to the floor.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by the League Office.
LaVine (MIN) and Crawford (LAC) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
Jordan (LAC) firms up as he sets the screen on Prince (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Wiggins (MIN) maintains legal guarding position and Johnson (LAC) slips while trying to create space on the inbounds play.
Jordan (LAC) makes incidental contact with Towns (MIN) after the release that does not affect his layup attempt.
Johnson (LAC) commits a take foul during rebounding against Prince (MIN).
Rubio (MIN) makes contact with Paul's (LAC) arm that affects his ability to catch the inbounds pass.
